\par
Kim rounded the end of the counter, intending to talk directly with the chef.\par
\par
Roger scrambled to his feet, and seeing Kim coming into the kitchen area. he tried to confront him. "You can't come back here," he said gamely. "Only employees are allowed .."\par
\par
